<lb n="0410a05"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0410a06"/>
<lb n="0410a07"/><head type="no">No. 168 [No. 152(38), No. 167]</head>
<lb n="0410a08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>佛說太子<note n="0410001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墓＝沐【三】＊</note><note n="0410001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墓＝沐【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0410001"><lem>墓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">沐</rdg></app>魄經<note n="0410002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開元…魄〕九字－【三】</note><note n="0410002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開元…魄〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410002" word-count="9"><lem><note place="inline">開元錄云沐魄或慕魄</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0410a09"/>
<lb n="0410a10"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0410003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【三】</note><note n="0410003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410003"><lem>月氏三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0410a11"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。<note n="0410004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛）＋告【三】</note><note n="0410004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛）＋告【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410004"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">佛告</rdg></app>
<lb n="0410a12"/>諸<note n="0410005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">比丘＝弟子【三】</note><note n="0410005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">比丘＝弟子【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410005"><lem>比丘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">弟子</rdg></app>。昔者有<note n="0410006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（王）＋【三】</note><note n="0410006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（王）＋【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410006"><lem>&lac;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>王名婆羅&CB00178;。王有一太子
<lb n="0410a13"/>字名<app type="＊" source="0410001"><lem>墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄。生有無窮之明。端正<note n="0410007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妙＝好【三】</note><note n="0410007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙＝好【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410007"><lem>妙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">好</rdg></app>潔無有
<lb n="0410a14"/>雙比。父母奇之供養瞻視。須其長大當為立
<lb n="0410a15"/>字。然太子結舌不語十有三歲。恬惔質朴志
<lb n="0410a16"/>若死灰<note n="0410008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意如＝直若【三】</note><note n="0410008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意如＝直若【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410008"><lem>意如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">直若</rdg></app>枯木。目不視色耳不聽音。狀
<lb n="0410a17"/>類瘖&CB00484;聾盲之人。於是父母患而<note n="0410009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">厭＝苦【三】</note><note n="0410009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厭＝苦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410009"><lem>厭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app>之。王
<lb n="0410a18"/>語夫人。當奈之何。此子將為他國所笑。夫
<lb n="0410a19"/>人語王。當召相師相之。知當語不。王即召
<lb n="0410a20"/>婆羅門師使相太子。婆羅門言。此子非是世
<lb n="0410a21"/>間人。為是熒惑耳。外為端正內懷不祥。危
<lb n="0410a22"/>國滅宗將至不久不可畜養。宜當生埋誅而
<lb n="0410a23"/>殺<note n="0410010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＋（今）【三】</note><note n="0410010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＋（今）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410010"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">之今</rdg></app>。不除此子則絕國嗣。王語夫人。當如
<lb n="0410a24"/>之何。今<note n="0410011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【三】</note><note n="0410011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔若〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410011"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不除<note n="0410012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此子＝之以往【三】</note><note n="0410012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此子＝之以往【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410012"><lem>此子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">之以往</rdg></app>恐後無復立<note n="0410013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔太〕－【三】</note><note n="0410013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔太〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410013"><lem>太</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>子。
<lb n="0410a25"/>於是夫人隨王所為。王即召國中大臣共議
<lb n="0410a26"/>之。一臣言。當遠徙深山無人之處。一臣言。
<lb n="0410a27"/>當沒深水中。一臣言。但當隨師所語。掘作深
<lb n="0410a28"/>坑而生埋之。王即隨是一臣所語。即召外陣
<lb n="0410a29"/>兵<note n="0410014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【三】</note><note n="0410014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝二【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410014"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>千<note n="0410015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔餘〕－【三】</note><note n="0410015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔餘〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410015"><lem>餘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>人。使掘地作藏。給<note n="0410016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝三十歲【三】</note><note n="0410016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝三十歲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410016"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三十歲</rdg></app>資糧侍以
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0168.0410b" n="0410b"/>
<lb n="0410b01"/>五僕。太子衣<note n="0410017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">服＝被【三】</note><note n="0410017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">服＝被【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410017"><lem>服</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">被</rdg></app>瓔珞<note n="0410018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珠寶＝寶蓋【三】</note><note n="0410018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珠寶＝寶蓋【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410018"><lem>珠寶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">寶蓋</rdg></app>盡還太子。於是
<lb n="0410b02"/>夫人心<note n="0410019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝用【三】</note><note n="0410019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲＝用【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410019"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">用</rdg></app>傷絕。我獨無相生子薄命<note n="0410020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝反【三】</note><note n="0410020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝反【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410020"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app>值
<lb n="0410b03"/>此殃。事不得止。涕淚哽咽不能自勝。於是復
<lb n="0410b04"/>送太子著正殿<note n="0410021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝前【三】＊</note><note n="0410021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上＝前【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0410021"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">前</rdg></app>五百夫人見太子端正姝
<lb n="0410b05"/>好無有雙比。皆言。太子何以不語而當生埋。
<lb n="0410b06"/>五百婇女見太子端正姝好。皆為太子作禮
<lb n="0410b07"/>而<note n="0410022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（太子）【三】</note><note n="0410022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＋（太子）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410022"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">言太子</rdg></app>。何以不語而當生埋。<note n="0410023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（各）＋各【三】</note><note n="0410023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（各）＋各【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410023"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">各各</rdg></app>為太子作<note n="0410024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其伎＝唱伎【宋】，倡妓【元】【明】</note><note n="0410024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其伎＝唱伎【宋】，＝倡妓【元】【明】</note><app n="0410024"><lem>其
<lb n="0410b08"/>伎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">唱伎</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">倡妓</rdg></app>樂。太子默然不觀不聽。<note n="0410025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝於是直【三】</note><note n="0410025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝於是直【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410025"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">於是直</rdg></app>送太子著外
<lb n="0410b09"/>殿<app type="＊" source="0410021"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">前</rdg></app>。五百大臣見太子端正姝好無有雙比。
<lb n="0410b10"/>前白大王。太子非是不語<note n="0410026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】</note><note n="0410026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410026"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>人。且<note n="0410027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝小【三】</note><note n="0410027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝小【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410027"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">小</rdg></app>宿留
<lb n="0410b11"/>語在不久。婆羅門<note n="0410028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝師【三】</note><note n="0410028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410028"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">師</rdg></app>。不可審信。王語大臣。
<lb n="0410b12"/>此是國事非卿所知。作藏<note n="0410029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】</note><note n="0410029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410029"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>訖來迎太子。
<lb n="0410b13"/>王語其僕。使太子載<note n="0410030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【三】</note><note n="0410030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔我〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410030"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>四望象車。令國中
<lb n="0410b14"/>人民就觀太子<note n="0410031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝儻【三】</note><note n="0410031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝儻【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410031"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">儻</rdg></app>語。<note n="0410032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（其）【三】</note><note n="0410032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若＋（其）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410032"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">若其</rdg></app>語者<note n="0410033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝更【三】</note><note n="0410033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝更【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410033"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">更</rdg></app>載來還。於
<lb n="0410b15"/>是太子<note n="0410034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乘＝昇【三】</note><note n="0410034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乘＝昇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410034"><lem>乘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">昇</rdg></app>車尋路。國中耆舊大臣皆宛轉車
<lb n="0410b16"/>前而言。太子。要當一語。若不語者便以車輾
<lb n="0410b17"/>我上過<note n="0410035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【三】</note><note n="0410035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔去〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410035"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。遮蠡虎賁扶避使過。遂<note n="0410036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝將【三】</note><note n="0410036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍＝將【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410036"><lem>侍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">將</rdg></app>太子<note n="0410037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遂到＝到其【三】</note><note n="0410037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遂到＝到其【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410037"><lem>
<lb n="0410b18"/>遂到</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">到其</rdg></app>藏所。時有數千萬人。皆<note n="0410038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＝送【三】</note><note n="0410038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隨＝送【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410038"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">送</rdg></app>太子往到藏
<lb n="0410b19"/>所。皆塞藏戶。太子復不得前。遮蠡虎賁麾人
<lb n="0410b20"/><note n="0410039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【三】</note><note n="0410039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝使【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410039"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>&CB00230;。太子<note n="0410040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適＋（欲）【三】</note><note n="0410040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">適＋（欲）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410040"><lem>適</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">適欲</rdg></app>前。飛鳥走獸復<note n="0410041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔驚〕－【三】</note><note n="0410041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔驚〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410041"><lem>驚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>來<note n="0410042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔前〕－【三】</note><note n="0410042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔前〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410042"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>遶
<lb n="0410b21"/>藏三匝。復塞藏戶。太子復不得前。於是<note n="0410043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔太子〕－【三】</note><note n="0410043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔太子〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410043"><lem>太
<lb n="0410b22"/>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>舉右手住而言。我正<note n="0410044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（欲）＋不【三】</note><note n="0410044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（欲）＋不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410044"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">欲不</rdg></app>語而當生埋。我適
<lb n="0410b23"/>欲語恐入地獄。我所以不語者。欲安身避害
<lb n="0410b24"/>濟神離苦。是以不語。而信<note n="0410045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誑＝狂【三】</note><note n="0410045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誑＝狂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410045"><lem>誑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">狂</rdg></app>詐之言。謂我
<lb n="0410b25"/>聾盲為實瘖&CB00484;。是時人民聞太<note n="0410046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（已）【三】</note><note n="0410046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（已）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410046"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">子已</rdg></app>語有絕妙
<lb n="0410b26"/>之<note n="0410047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＝聲【三】</note><note n="0410047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音＝聲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410047"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">聲</rdg></app>世所希聞。行者為止。坐者為<note n="0410048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】</note><note n="0410048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410048"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>起。皆
<lb n="0410b27"/>言。太子神聖乃爾。皆前叩頭求恩悔過。原赦
<lb n="0410b28"/>我罪。其僕聞之歡喜踊躍。馳白大王。太子已
<lb n="0410b29"/>語。上徹蒼天下徹黃泉。飛鳥走獸皆來伏聽
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0168.0410c" n="0410c"/>
<lb n="0410c01"/>於太子前。王聞太子語歡<note n="0410049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欣＝喜【三】</note><note n="0410049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欣＝喜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410049"><lem>欣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">喜</rdg></app>踊躍。即與夫
<lb n="0410c02"/>人<note n="0410050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">駕＝乘【三】</note><note n="0410050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">駕＝乘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410050"><lem>駕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">乘</rdg></app>四望象車。往迎太子。太子顧<note n="0410051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視＝見【三】</note><note n="0410051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視＝見【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410051"><lem>視</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>父王
<lb n="0410c03"/>下車避道。四拜而起而言。勞屈父王遠來見
<lb n="0410c04"/>迎。今日父子<note n="0410052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已〕－【三】</note><note n="0410052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔已〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410052"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>生相棄捐。恩愛已乖骨肉
<lb n="0410c05"/><note n="0410053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【明】</note><app n="0410053"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>離。其義甚愆不可聽觀。王語太子。<note n="0410054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不可不可＝吾無智慧信任邪師忽致於此吾之愚癡其過深矣【三】</note><note n="0410054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不可不可＝吾無智慧信任邪師忽致於此吾之愚癡其過深矣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410054"><lem>不可
<lb n="0410c06"/>不可</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">吾無智慧信任邪師忽致於此吾之愚癡其過深矣</rdg></app>。汝為智者當原不及。共還入國舉位與
<lb n="0410c07"/>汝。我自避退。太子答言。<note n="0410055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＋（已）【三】</note><note n="0410055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＋（已）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410055"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">我已</rdg></app>曾為國王用行
<lb n="0410c08"/>有缺漏故。下入地獄六萬餘歲。蒸&CB00827;剝裂其
<lb n="0410c09"/>痛難忍。當此之時。父母寧能知我地獄苦痛
<lb n="0410c10"/>劇不。寧能分取我身上痛不。我厭<note n="0410056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔畏〕－【三】</note><note n="0410056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔畏〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410056"><lem>畏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>地獄
<lb n="0410c11"/>苦。是以結舌不語十有三歲。冀得免瑕除去
<lb n="0410c12"/><note n="0410057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">垢＝污【三】</note><note n="0410057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">垢＝污【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410057"><lem>垢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">污</rdg></app>穢。出於<note n="0410058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塵埃＝垢塵【三】</note><note n="0410058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塵埃＝垢塵【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410058"><lem>塵埃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">垢塵</rdg></app>之外不與罪會。除憂去累
<lb n="0410c13"/>念生若寄。不可<note n="0410059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">選軟＝潠濡【宋】</note><app n="0410059"><lem>選軟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">潠濡</rdg></app>去道日遠。高翔遠逝
<lb n="0410c14"/>自濟於世。世間無常恍<note n="0410060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惚＝忽【宋】【元】</note><app n="0410060"><lem>惚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">忽</rdg></app>如夢。室家歡<note n="0410061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娛＝喜【三】</note><note n="0410061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娛＝喜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410061"><lem>娛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">喜</rdg></app>
<lb n="0410c15"/>須臾間耳。歡樂暫有憂苦延長。王知太子意
<lb n="0410c16"/>堅志固。遂聽學道。於是太子棄國捐王。入
<lb n="0410c17"/>山求道思惟禪定。壽終即生<note n="0410062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兜術＝第四兜率【三】</note><note n="0410062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兜術＝第四兜率【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410062"><lem>兜術</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">第四兜率</rdg></app>天上。畢
<lb n="0410c18"/>天之壽下生世間。為迦維羅衛王作太子。自
<lb n="0410c19"/>致<note n="0410063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝作【三】</note><note n="0410063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝作【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410063"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">作</rdg></app>佛。佛告阿難。<note n="0410064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾＝是【三】</note><note n="0410064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾＝是【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410064"><lem>爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>時太子<app type="＊" source="0410001"><lem>墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄者我身
<lb n="0410c20"/>是也。<note n="0410065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】</note><note n="0410065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410065"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>時父王者今閱頭檀<note n="0410066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是也〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0410066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是也〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0410066"><lem>是也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。是時母
<lb n="0410c21"/>者今摩耶<app type="＊" source="0410066"><lem>是也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>。是時侍我五僕者<note n="0410067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今）＋阿【三】</note><note n="0410067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（今）＋阿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410067"><lem>阿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">今阿</rdg></app>若拘
<lb n="0410c22"/>&CB00444;等是<note n="0410068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】</note><note n="0410068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410068"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。是時婆羅門欲生埋我者今調達
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0168.0411a" n="0411a"/>
<lb n="0411a01"/>是也。我與調達世世有怨。佛說經<note n="0411001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訖＝已【三】</note><note n="0411001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訖＝已【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0411001"><lem>訖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>。諸弟
<lb n="0411a02"/>子<note n="0411002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】</note><note n="0411002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0411002"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>天龍鬼神帝王人民皆大歡喜。為佛作
<lb n="0411a03"/>禮</p>
<lb n="0411a04"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說太子<app type="＊" source="0410001"><lem>墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄經</jhead></juan></div1>
